OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fbright evening, but then turning
OL,7,Fcloudy with patchy rain and drizzle
OL,8,Fdeveloping towards midnight, though
OL,9,Fmost places staying dry. Breezy and
OL,10,Fmild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FRain clearing south early in
OL,13,Fthe morning to leave a sunny day for
OL,14,Fmost. Winds falling light as the day
OL,15,Fprogresses so a pleasant afternoon to
OL,16,Fcome.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
